        <div class="forum_topic_posts_info_body">
          The tragedy of the reality of Ebola.

By Will Wintercross
<a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/ebola/11352429/Ebola-crisis-Sierra-Leones-cemetary-full-of-children.html">Ebola crisis in Sierra Leone creates cementary full of children</a>

